workout.name: Burpees
workout.desc: From standing position, drop down so that your chest touches the ground. From this position you goal is to place you feet where your hands are and then jump up and clap you hands over your head.

workout.name: Chopups
workout.desc: Lay down on the ground with your arms streched out over your head. In one motion move your arms upward and stand up

workout.name: Getups
workout.desc: From laying flat on your back, sit up with you legs still straight. Now, turn you body to your right side and place your hands on the ground about a shoulders width apart. Now, pull in you right leg so that your foot almost touches you right buttocks. Next, with the weight of your body on you hands move your right leg under you body and place it to the right. You should now be facing your right side with you knees bent. Stand up straight and strech you hands up over your head. Now the revers movement will take place, so start by bending you knees and placing you hands on the ground. Take you right leg and move it straight through

workout.name: HipSwitches

workout.name: JumpingJacks
workout.desc: From standing upright position, extend your arms over your head and at the same time push you legs out to the sides. You arms should be straight during the whole workout to warm up the shoulders
